(1. Executive Summary) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 628.25 Tm
(fun.lol is a customizable public profile platform where users can create a public bio page, add) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 614.75 Tm
(visual and audio media, connect with friends, join tribes, chat with tribe members, and play mini-) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 601.25 Tm
(games from a private dashboard. The current product blends a personal identity page with) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 587.75 Tm
(lightweight social and entertainment features.) Tj
/F2 15 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 563.25 Tm
(2. Product Vision) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 539.00 Tm
(The long-term vision is for fun.lol to become a highly personalized social identity hub. Users) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 525.50 Tm
(should be able to express themselves through media-rich profiles, share one public link, keep up) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 512.00 Tm
(with friends, create small communities, and enjoy interactive experiences without leaving the) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 498.50 Tm
(platform.) Tj
/F2 15 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 474.00 Tm
(3. Target Users) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 449.75 Tm
(- Creators who want a personalized profile link.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 436.25 Tm
(- Gamers who enjoy expressive profiles and mini-games.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 422.75 Tm
(- Social users who want a lightweight friend graph.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 409.25 Tm
(- Friend groups who want private-ish spaces around shared identity.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 395.75 Tm
(- Community or tribe members who want a shared group and chat.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 382.25 Tm
(- Public visitors who open a user's profile link.) Tj
/F2 15 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 360.75 Tm
(4. Problem Statement) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 336.50 Tm
(Many profile-link tools are static, generic, and disconnected from the user's actual social) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 323.00 Tm
(experience. fun.lol solves this by combining profile customization, media, friend requests, tribe) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 309.50 Tm
(communities, tribe chats, and mini-games in one lightweight web platform.) Tj
/F2 15 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 285.00 Tm
(5. Product Goals) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 260.75 Tm
(- Enable personal profile customization.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 247.25 Tm
(- Support public profile sharing by handle.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 233.75 Tm
(- Make social discovery and friend connection simple.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 220.25 Tm
(- Provide tribe/community engagement.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 206.75 Tm
(- Add mini-game entertainment inside the dashboard.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 193.25 Tm
(- Preserve a strong dark, animated, profile-first brand feel.) Tj
/F2 15 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 171.75 Tm
(6. Non-Goals) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 147.50 Tm
(The current version does not include:) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 131.00 Tm
(- A full social media feed.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 117.50 Tm
(- Payment or subscription systems.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 104.00 Tm
(- Advanced moderation dashboard.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 90.50 Tm
(- Native mobile app.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 77.00 Tm
(- Enterprise admin portal.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 48.00 63.50 Tm
(- End-to-end encrypted messaging.) Tj
